Image Vs Container

| Feature          | Docker Image                     | Docker Container                            |
| ---------------- | -------------------------------- | ------------------------------------------- |
| Type             | Blueprint / template             | Running instance                            |
| Mutability       | Immutable                        | Mutable (has a writable layer)              |
| Purpose          | Defines environment and app      | Executes the app                            |
| Storage          | Stored on disk                   | Lives in memory while running               |
| Multiple copies? | Reused to create many containers | Yes, many containers can run from one image |


